keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map k scrollDown
map i scrollUp
map j scrollLeft
map l scrollRight

map h enterInsertMode
map J goBack

map <a-j> previousTab
map <a-l> nextTab
map <c-d> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-u> scrollFullPageUp

map M Marks.activateGotoMode
searchEngines:
